snippet.title: Ultimate Mortal Kombat DS Online in 2019 (Real DS Capture)
snippet.description:
People demanded we post more MKDS online footage, so here it is: Mortal Kombat DS online footage! Watch it and marvel at our inability to get a single Fatality right, even though the button combos are right there. We're using this method to connect to Wiimmfi: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sh0AZR-tKwM

 Matches played:

01:08 Sonya vs. Reptile
02:30 Sheeva vs. Sub-Zero
04:37 Kitana vs. Raiden
06:19 Jade vs. Stryker
08:14 Smoke vs. Jax
09:49 Kabal vs. Liu Kang
11:31 Nightwolf vs. Shang Tsung

NEXT: Puzzle Kombat!

Wanna play DS online with us? Join our Discord and let's give it a shot (no promises): https://discord.gg/4qh7kNu

(Played on a real Nintendo DS, captured through a Loopy DS capture card.)
